fix(turbopack): Consider scoping of `var` declarations (#77954)

### What?

Fix turbopack es analyzer, for the case below

```js
const shouldRun = () => false;

export default function run() {
  if (shouldRun()) {
    var x = true;
  }
  if (x) {
    return 'should not run';
  }
  return 'should run';
}

```

### Why?

### How?

Fixes #77126 
Closes PACK-4159

